1. iri me dug₃-dug₃-ga barag mah nam-lugal-la
#lem: iri[city]; me[Being]; dug[good]; barag[sanctum]; mah[great]; namlugal[kingship]
#etcsl: line-id=1

2. eš₃ urim₅{ki} gu₂-gal ki#-en-gi-ra ki kug-ga du₃-a
#lem: eš[shrine]; Urim[1]SN; gugal[foremost]; Kengir[1]; ki[place]; kug[pure]; du[build]
#etcsl: line-id=2

3. iri bad₃ gal ki ŋar-ra-zu! abzu-ta mu₂-a
#lem: iri[city]; bad[wall]; gal[big]; ki[place]; ŋar[put]; abzu[(cosmic) underground water]; mu[grow]
#etcsl: line-id=3

4. iri an-gin₇ sig₇-ga hi-li gur₃-ru ki gal-la gun₃-gun₃
#lem: iri[city]; an[sky]; sissig[green-yellow]; hili[attractiveness]; gur[lift]; ki[place]; gal[big]; gunu[speckled]
#etcsl: line-id=4

5. eš₃ urim₅{ki} ŋi₆-par₄ ki ŋar-ra ki-tuš an {d}en-lil₂-la₂
#lem: eš[shrine]; Urim[1]SN; ŋipar[cloister]; ki[place]; ŋar[put]; kituš[dwelling place]; An[1]DN; Enlil[1]DN
#etcsl: line-id=5

6. e₂-gal mah-zu! e₂-kiš-nu-ŋal₂ šag₄-ga nam tar-ra
#lem: egal[palace]; mah[great]; Ekišnuŋal[1]TN; šag[heart]; nam[fate]; tar[cut]
#etcsl: line-id=6

7. dub-la₂-zu me-lem₄ du₈-du₈-a kur-kur-ra dirig-ga
#lem: dubla[gate tower]; melim[frightening splendor]; du[spread]; kur[mountain(s)]; dirig[make more than]
#etcsl: line-id=7

8. gi-gun₄-na-bi dungu babbar-gin₇ an-šag₄-ga u₆ di
#lem: giguna[high sacred terrace]; dungu[cloud]; babbar[white]; anšag[the interior of heaven]; u[admiration]; di[speak]
#etcsl: line-id=8

9. {ŋiš}RU-bi nim ŋir₂-ŋir₂-e-gin₇ eš₃ šag₄-ga kumₓ(PA)-kumₓ(PA)-mu
#lem: RU[an architectural feature]; nim[lightning]; ŋir[flash]; eš[shrine]; šag[heart]; kun[shine brightly]
#etcsl: line-id=9

10. 1 gud {ŋiš}šudul₄-a-gin₇ ur₂ gur-ra X kug da-ra-ga
#lem: n; gud[bull]; šudul[yoke]; ur[loin]; gur[thick]; X; kug[purify]; X
#etcsl: line-id=10

11. {ŋiš}banšur sikil-la# ki aŋ₂ {d}suen-na
#lem: banšur[table]; sikil[pure]; ki[place]; aŋ[measure]; Suen[1]DN
#etcsl: line-id=11

12. e₂-kiš-nu-ŋal₂ {ŋiš}banšur sikil#-la ki aŋ₂ {d}suen-na
#lem: Ekišnuŋal[1]TN; banšur[table]; sikil[pure]; ki[place]; aŋ[measure]; Suen[1]DN
#etcsl: line-id=12

